# UDeltio API
UDeltio API is a message board service

# UDeltio API Root [/api/v1.0/]





# Group Board

## Board [/boards/{id}]
A single Board object.

The Board resource has the following attributes:

- id
- name
- public
- subscribers
- tags

The *id* state is assigned by the UDeltio API at the moment of creation.


+ Parameters
    + id (required, Number, `1`) ... ID of the Board

+ Model (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "id": 1,
                "name": "Rock Climbing",
                "public": true,
                "subscribers": [1, 2, 3],
                "tags": [12, 42, 85]
            }

    + Schema
        
            {
                "type": "object",
                "required": true,
                "properties": {
                    "id": {
                        "type": "number"
                    },
                    "name": {
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    "public": {
                        "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "subscribers": {
                        "type": "array"
                    },
                    "tags": {
                        "type": "array"
                    }
                },
                "required": [
                    "id",
                    "name",
                    "public",
                    "subscribers",
                    "tags"
                ]
            }

### Get Board [GET]
+ Response 200

    [Board][]


### Update Board [PUT]
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "Rock Climbing",
            "public": true,
            "subscribers": [1, 2, 3],
            "tags": [12, 42, 85]
        }

+ Response 200

    [Board][]


### Delete Board [DELETE]
+ Response 204


